Osborne Says Successful Euro is in Britain’s Interest

-- B y   J e n n i f e r   R y a n
-- 
2011-09-16T08:35:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/osborne-says-successful-euro-is-in-britain-s-interest.html
U.K. Chancellor of the Exchequer
 George Osborne  said a successful euro is in Britain’s interest,
and he urged leaders in the region to implement quickly the
accord from July 21. He spoke at a conference in Manchester
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
